        "text": "Forgot to post this, what with all the _christmas chaos…_\n\nIn just 16 hours (at time of writing, _of course_, you _lovely pedants_) we'll have the final FoC virtual meetup of 2025.\n\nHere's the <https:\/\/luma.com\/lbnc5ear|Luma page> if you want to RSVP for a reminder. The meetup starts at <https:\/\/time.is\/1800_31_DEC_2025_in_UTC?FoC_Virtual_meetup|18:00 UTC>.\n\nWe'll have 3 demos:\n\n• I'm going to demo a little tangible sandbox I made for playing with 1-bit error-diffusion dither kernels, since these things are _inherently spatial_ in surprising &amp; fun ways\n• <@U05UK5T7LPP> is going to show Dendryscope, a tool \"meant for narrative designers to playtest their games with an intelligent interface, [which] happens to be a fun use case for answer set programming via clingo in the browser.\"\n• <@U02QC0PPER3> will \"demo (and try to motivate) some <https:\/\/model-view-self-modify.netlify.app\/README|self-modifying code ideas> I've been playing with\"\nWould love to see you there, especially if anyone happens to be tuning in at midnight local time :)\n\nWhen the time comes, join here: <https:\/\/ivanish.ca\/zoom>",
